Package org.opensaml.saml1.core

Interfaces for SAML 1.0 and 1.1 types and elements.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Action Interface describing how a SAML1.1 Action element behaves
Advice This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 Advice element behaves.
Assertion This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 Assertion element behaves.
AssertionArtifact This interface is for the SAML1 AssertionArtifact extention point.
AssertionIDReference This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 AssertionIDReference element behaves.
Attribute This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 Attribute element behaves.
AttributeDesignator This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 AttributeDesignator element behaves.
AttributeQuery Description of the behaviour of the AttributeQuery element
AttributeStatement This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 AttributeStatement element behaves.
AttributeValue This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 AttributeValue element behaves.
Audience This interface describes how ab object representing a SAML1 Audience element will behave.
AudienceRestrictionCondition This interface describes how ab object representing a SAML1 AudienceRestrictionCondition element will behave.
AuthenticationQuery Description of the behaviour of the AuthenticationQuery element
AuthenticationStatement This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 AuthenticationStatment element behaves.
AuthorityBinding Interface to define how a AuthorityBinding <\code> element behaves
AuthorizationDecisionQuery Description of the behaviour of the AuthorizationDecisionQuery element
AuthorizationDecisionStatement This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 AuthorizationDecisionStatement element behaves.
Condition This interface describes how a object representing a SAML1 Condition element will behave.
Conditions This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 Conditions element behaves.
ConfirmationMethod This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 ConfirmationMethod element behaves.
DoNotCacheCondition This interface describes how ab object representing a SAML1 DoNotCacheCondition element will behave.
Evidence Interface describing how a SAML1.1 Evidence element behaves
Evidentiary Marker interface for element types that can constitute evidence within a @{org.opensaml.saml1.core.Evidence} object.
NameIdentifier Interface to define how a NameIdentifier element behaves.
Query This interface is for the SAML1 Query extention point.
Request This interface defines how the SAML1 Request objects behave.
RequestAbstractType This interface describes the base class for types derived from RequestAbstractType
RespondWith This interface defines how the (deprecated) RespondWith element would behave.
Response This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 Response element behaves.
ResponseAbstractType This interface defines the base class for type derived from the SAML1 ResponseAbstractType .
Statement This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 Statement element behaves.
Status This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 Status element behaves.
StatusCode This interface defines how the object representing a SAML 1 StatusCode element behaves.
StatusDetail Interface to describe how a StatusDetail <\code> element behaves
StatusMessage This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 StatusMessage element behaves.
Subject Interface to describe how the Subject elements work.
SubjectConfirmation Interface to define how a SubjectConfirmation element behaves
SubjectConfirmationData This interface defines how the object representing a SAML1 SubjectConfirmationData element behaves.
SubjectLocality Interface to define how a SubjectLocality element behaves.
SubjectQuery This interface is for the SAML1 SubjectQuery extention point.
SubjectStatement Interface to descibe how the anchor point SubjectStatement would work.
 

Class Summary
DecisionTypeEnumeration A type safe "enumeration" of AuthorizationDecisionStatement Decision types.
 

Package org.opensaml.saml1.core Description

Interfaces for SAML 1.0 and 1.1 types and elements.

Information on using this library can be found in the User's Manual and information on extending its functionality can be found in the Developer's Manual.
